Customer sign-in
================



Verify that a valid customer can Sign-in
----------------
tags: sign-up, customer
* Go to demo store
* Check that store is up
* Sign in as an existing customer
* Verify that Notes module is available

Verify that a user with an invalid password cannot Sign-in
------------------------
* Go to demo store
* Check that store is up
* Attempt sign-in as an invalid customer (password)
* Verify that error message is shown
* Verify that error message matches design

Verify that a user with an invalid username cannot Sign-in
------------------------
* Go to demo store
* Check that store is up
* Attempt sign-in as an invalid customer (user)
* Verify that error message is shown
* Verify that error message matches design